# Upstream-Aware Source Editing

This repo is a fork of huggingface/lerobot. Files under `src/lerobot/` come from upstream and are periodically synced via `git merge upstream/main`. Edit them freely when it's the right approach -- just be aware that changes here may need conflict resolution during upstream merges.

## Currently modified upstream files

- `src/lerobot/scripts/lerobot_record.py` -- progress bar, action debug logging, headless fixes
- `src/lerobot/utils/control_utils.py` -- stdin-based headless keyboard controls

See `ledream_changelog.md` section "Modified Upstream Files" for details.

## Guidelines

- Mark custom code blocks with `# DP:` comments so they're easy to find during merge conflict resolution
- Update `ledream_changelog.md` when modifying upstream files
- When adding substantial new functionality, consider whether a separate file (under `scripts/`, `configs/`, etc.) would work -- additive files never cause merge conflicts
